    <item>
      <title>随着关税风险迫在眉睫，美国通货膨胀将保持粘性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/us-inflation-set-to-stay-sticky-as-tariff-risk-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国消费者的价格可能在2月的速度上涨，这说明了美联储官员的通货膨胀进展。他们可能会满足于保持旁观者的范围，以评估特朗普政府的旋风。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/us-inflation-set-to-stay-sticky-as-tariff-risk-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对加拿大油菜油，猪肉设定了报复性关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/china-imposes-retaliatory-tariffs-on-canada-rapeseed-oil-pork</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，随着贸易战争的升级，它将对加拿大的油菜油，猪肉和海鲜进口征收报复性关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-08/china-imposes-retaliatory-tariffs-on-canada-rapeseed-oil-pork</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 01:27:50 GMT</pubDate>
